RUN |8 BUILDLABEL=f5152314.01 USER=was PROFILE_NAME=AppSrv01 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 HOST_NAME=localhost SERVER_NAME=server1 ADMIN_USER_NAME=wsadmin /bin/sh -c useradd $USER -g 0 -m --uid 1001   && mkdir /opt/IBM   && chmod -R +x /work/*   && mkdir /etc/websphere   && mkdir /work/config   && chown -R 1001:0 /work /opt/IBM /etc/websphere   && chmod -R g+rwx /work # buildkit

RUN |8 BUILDLABEL=f5152314.01 USER=was PROFILE_NAME=AppSrv01 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 HOST_NAME=localhost SERVER_NAME=server1 ADMIN_USER_NAME=wsadmin /bin/sh -c /work/create_profile.sh   && find /opt/IBM -user was ! -perm -g=w -print0 | xargs -0 chmod g+w   && chmod -R g+rwx /home/was/.java/ # buildkit

RUN |8 BUILDLABEL=f5152314.01 USER=was PROFILE_NAME=AppSrv01 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 HOST_NAME=localhost SERVER_NAME=server1 ADMIN_USER_NAME=wsadmin /bin/sh -c sed -i 's/genericJvmArguments=""/genericJvmArguments="-Xnoloa"/' /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/$PROFILE_NAME/config/cells/$CELL_NAME/nodes/$NODE_NAME/servers/$SERVER_NAME/server.xml # buildkit

RUN |8 BUILDLABEL=f5152314.01 USER=was PROFILE_NAME=AppSrv01 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 HOST_NAME=localhost SERVER_NAME=server1 ADMIN_USER_NAME=wsadmin /bin/sh -c ln -s /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/${PROFILE_NAME}/logs /logs && chown 1001:0 /logs # buildkit

RUN |8 BUILDLABEL=f5152314.01 USER=was PROFILE_NAME=AppSrv01 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 HOST_NAME=localhost SERVER_NAME=server1 ADMIN_USER_NAME=wsadmin /bin/sh -c rm /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/$PROFILE_NAME/config/cells/$CELL_NAME/nodes/$NODE_NAME/trust.p12  && rm /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/$PROFILE_NAME/config/cells/$CELL_NAME/nodes/$NODE_NAME/key.p12  && rm /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/$PROFILE_NAME/config/cells/$CELL_NAME/nodes/$NODE_NAME/root-key.p12  && rm /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/$PROFILE_NAME/etc/trust.p12  && rm /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/$PROFILE_NAME/etc/key.p12 # buildkit

|8 ADMIN_USER_NAME=wsadmin BUILDLABEL=f5021945.04 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 HOST_NAME=localhost NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 PROFILE_NAME=AppSrv01 SERVER_NAME=server1 USER=was /bin/sh -c useradd $USER -g 0 -m --uid 1001   && mkdir /opt/IBM   && chmod -R +x /work/*   && mkdir /etc/websphere   && mkdir /work/config   && chown -R 1001:0 /work /opt/IBM /etc/websphere   && chmod -R g+rwx /work

|5 BUILDLABEL=f5021945.04 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 HOST_NAME=localhost NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 USER=was /bin/sh -c /work/create_profile.sh   && find /opt/IBM -user was ! -perm -g=w -print0 | xargs -0 chmod g+w   && chmod -R g+rwx /home/was/.java/

|5 BUILDLABEL=f5021945.04 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 HOST_NAME=localhost NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 USER=was /bin/sh -c ln -s /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/${PROFILE_NAME}/logs /logs && chown 1001:0 /logs

history.created_by: /bin/sh -c #(nop)  LABEL maintainer=Glenn Marcy <gmarcy@us.ibm.com> BuildLabel=f5021945.04 vendor=IBM name=IBM WebSphere Traditional version=9.0.5.2 summary=Image for WebSphere Traditional and UBI description=This image contains the WebSphere Traditional runtime with Red Hat UBI as the base OS.
|1 BUILDLABEL=f5021945.04 /bin/sh -c dnf --disableplugin=subscription-manager install -y openssl wget unzip diffutils procps

|8 ADMIN_USER_NAME=wsadmin BUILDLABEL=f5021945.04 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 HOST_NAME=localhost NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 PROFILE_NAME=AppSrv01 SERVER_NAME=server1 USER=was /bin/sh -c useradd $USER -g 0 -m --uid 1001   && mkdir /opt/IBM   && chmod -R +x /work/*   && mkdir /etc/websphere   && mkdir /work/config   && chown -R 1001:0 /work /opt/IBM /etc/websphere   && chmod -R g+rwx /work

|5 BUILDLABEL=f5021945.04 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 HOST_NAME=localhost NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 USER=was /bin/sh -c /work/create_profile.sh   && find /opt/IBM -user was ! -perm -g=w -print0 | xargs -0 chmod g+w   && chmod -R g+rwx /home/was/.java/

|5 BUILDLABEL=f5021945.04 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 HOST_NAME=localhost NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 USER=was /bin/sh -c sed -i 's/genericJvmArguments=""/genericJvmArguments="-Xnoloa"/' /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/$PROFILE_NAME/config/cells/$CELL_NAME/nodes/$NODE_NAME/servers/$SERVER_NAME/server.xml

|5 BUILDLABEL=f5021945.04 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 HOST_NAME=localhost NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 USER=was /bin/sh -c ln -s /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/${PROFILE_NAME}/logs /logs && chown 1001:0 /logs

|8 ADMIN_USER_NAME=wsadmin BUILDLABEL=f5082121.02 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 HOST_NAME=localhost NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 PROFILE_NAME=AppSrv01 SERVER_NAME=server1 USER=was /bin/sh -c useradd $USER -g 0 -m --uid 1001   && mkdir /opt/IBM   && chmod -R +x /work/*   && mkdir /etc/websphere   && mkdir /work/config   && chown -R 1001:0 /work /opt/IBM /etc/websphere   && chmod -R g+rwx /work

|5 BUILDLABEL=f5082121.02 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 HOST_NAME=localhost NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 USER=was /bin/sh -c /work/create_profile.sh   && find /opt/IBM -user was ! -perm -g=w -print0 | xargs -0 chmod g+w   && chmod -R g+rwx /home/was/.java/

|5 BUILDLABEL=f5082121.02 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 HOST_NAME=localhost NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 USER=was /bin/sh -c sed -i 's/genericJvmArguments=""/genericJvmArguments="-Xnoloa"/' /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/$PROFILE_NAME/config/cells/$CELL_NAME/nodes/$NODE_NAME/servers/$SERVER_NAME/server.xml

|5 BUILDLABEL=f5082121.02 CELL_NAME=DefaultCell01 HOST_NAME=localhost NODE_NAME=DefaultNode01 USER=was /bin/sh -c ln -s /opt/IBM/WebSphere/AppServer/profiles/${PROFILE_NAME}/logs /logs && chown 1001:0 /logs
